I recently picked up a @corosglobal VERTIX GPS watch to keep track of how far I go and help me train for my next adventure. #africa #travel #nonprofit #travelstoke #tenba

I met these two boys at an orphanage in the Ivory Coast. They were beyond excited to take a picture and I probably would have missed this moment if they didnt run up to me yelling "photo photo photo". Once they calmed down and thought I'd put the camera away I got their attention and quickly snapped this portrait.

#tenba #travelstoke #optoutside #africa #travelphotography #travelgram #portrait #nonprofit

This boy is an orphan at an orphanage in Divo, Cote D'ivore. He isnt a day over 13. The shoes in his hand were given to him by a volunteer at @operationinternational who are providing the orphanage with supplies and funding to become self sustaining.
